Hi All, We would really appreciate it, if tomorrow you are coming for
the drive through you would donate some Cat food. Kate will ensure it gets to the Cork Animal Care Society in time
for Christmas. They are a sanctuary for Cats. No tin too small or too big.
Thank you so much for your generosity today and all
at such short notice, you are fantastic.
